'''西蒙·卡洛'''（{{lang-en|Simon Phillip Hugh Callow}}，{{bd|1949年|6月15日}}）<ref name=Independent1999 >{{cite news |title=Queen's Birthday Honours: The Full List |date=12 June 1999 |newspaper=[[The_Independent|The Independent]] |url=http://www.independent.co.uk/news/queens-birthday-honours-the-full-list-1099582.html |accessdate=2016-03-23 |archive-date=2020-11-27 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201127053358/https://www.independent.co.uk/news/queens-birthday-honours-the-full-list-1099582.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>，全名'''西蒙·菲利浦·休·卡洛'''（{{lang-en|Simon Phillip Hugh Callow}}），是[[英國|英國]]演員。

== 經歷 ==
=== 早年生活 ===
出生在[[倫敦|倫敦]][[斯特里漢姆|斯特里漢姆]]<ref>{{cite web | title=Simon Callow Biography | url=http://www.filmreference.com/film/69/Simon-Callow.html | work=filmreference | year=2008 | accessdate=1 September 2008 | archive-date=2018-08-07 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180807085943/http://www.filmreference.com/film/69/Simon-Callow.html | dead-url=no }}</ref>。他成長在一個[[天主教|天主教]]家庭。母親伊馮娜·瑪麗（娘家姓吉斯）為丹麥及德國裔，是位秘書；父親尼爾·弗朗西斯·卡洛擁英格蘭及法國血統，是名商人<ref>{{cite web | title=Simon Callow Biography | url=http://www.filmreference.com/film/69/Simon-Callow.html | work=filmreference | year=2008 | access-date=1 September 2008 | archive-date=2018-08-07 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180807085943/http://www.filmreference.com/film/69/Simon-Callow.html | dead-url=no }}</ref><ref name=tet>{{cite news |url=https://news.google.com/newspapers?id=oBIzAAAAIBAJ&pg=6599,4272070&dq=owner-never-got-to-see-team-the-big-one&hl=en |title=Spending time in Africa shaped who Simon Callow is today |first=Luaine |last=Lee |date=30 October 2002 |location=Wilmington, North Carolina |page=9 |newspaper=Star News |accessdate=2021-11-29 |archive-date=2021-11-29 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20211129020309/https://news.google.com/newspapers?id=oBIzAAAAIBAJ&pg=6599,4272070&dq=owner-never-got-to-see-team-the-big-one&hl=en |dead-url=no }}</ref>。卡洛曾入讀[[北愛爾蘭|北愛爾蘭]]的[[貝爾法斯特女王大學|貝爾法斯特女王大學]]，並熱心於{{le|北愛爾蘭民權運動|Northern Ireland civil rights movement}}，及後在{{le|倫敦戲劇中心|Drama Centre London}}繼續學業<ref name=jones>Jonathan Jones (30 September 2011). [https://www.theguardian.com/artanddesign/2011/sep/30/saint-martins-kings-cross-premises Saint Martins emerges blinking in bright new home. But is it art?: King's Cross premises a far cry from Soho 'hell', but some students fear college will have lost its charm] {{Wayback|url=https://www.theguardian.com/artanddesign/2011/sep/30/saint-martins-kings-cross-premises |date=20201012215445 }}. ''The Guardian''. Accessed August 2013.</ref>。

===私人生活===
卡洛是一名已[[出櫃|出櫃]]的同志，被《[[獨立報|獨立報]]》於2007年選為英國排名第二十八位最具影響力的同性戀人士，並於2016年6月與塞巴斯蒂安·福克斯（Sebastian Fox）結婚<ref>{{cite interview |title=Simon Callow: 'Marriage is a remarkable thing to happen to someone at the age of 67' |url=http://www.thetimes.co.uk/article/simon-callow-marriage-is-a-remarkable-thing-to-happen-to-someone-at-67-but-im-not-decrepit-qz9rl0lw2 |url-access=subscription |interviewer=Nick Curtis |website=[[The_Times|The Times]] |date=31 December 2016 |access-date=2021-11-29 |archive-date=2021-11-29 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20211129021903/https://www.thetimes.co.uk/article/simon-callow-marriage-is-a-remarkable-thing-to-happen-to-someone-at-67-but-im-not-decrepit-qz9rl0lw2 |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{cite interview |url=http://www.radiotimes.com/news/2016-07-20/simon-callow-on-love-and-loss |title=Simon Callow on love and loss |interviewer=Michael Hodges |website=RadioTimes |date=20 July 2016 |access-date=2021-11-29 |archive-date=2020-08-14 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200814081145/https://www.radiotimes.com/news/2016-07-20/simon-callow-on-love-and-loss/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

